question: Rachel purchased a kit for making a skateboard ramp. Which of the following is most important to have for putting the ramp together?
candidate_answers: (A) a picture showing the colors of different ramp parts (B) a diagram showing some ways to use the ramp (C) a list of prices for other available kits (D) a set of instructions for the kit materials
answer: a picture showing the colors of different ramp parts
label: A
